INTRODUCTION:

Population Forecast for African Countries

SUMMARY:

We gathered secondary data for the populcation forecast of some African Countries from Year 1950 - Year 2020 and in the Power BI presentation the forecasted data for the 3 countries compared (Nigeria, Sudan and Kenya) gives Nigeria as the highest populated country as at Year 2020.

We used both the line chart and bar chart to display the forecasted data for each country.
